data.name: Quick Apple Cranberry Sauce
data.quickTastyDescription: A tangy and sweet sauce that pairs perfectly with turkey or can be enjoyed as a refreshing side dish.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a medium saucepan, combine the cranberries, chopped apple, sugar, and water.
